<a href="http://www.pspad.com/">PsPAD</a> for Windows (out-of-box; see also the alternative
<a href="https://gist.github.com/alex-konovalov/68cea8bd9332a06e08b1#file-gap-ini">GAP.INI</a>
file by <mixer person="Alexander Konovalov" data="name_link"/>)
</p>
</li>

